summary: This is a racemenu preset for a character I made, Jade Thorne. She has one of the most perfect faces I have ever created, so she may also be one of the best starter meshes out there to start building your own female Imperial characters after.
descriptionHtml:
*THIS IS A RACEMENU PRESET*
This is also a preset for the IMPERIAL race only. (Otherwise Jade looks deformed)

[i]Name: Jade Thorne
Race: Imperial
Age: 18
Eyes: Blue
Hair: Brown[/i]

To make Jade look exactly like in the screenshots above, I highly suggest downloading the following mods:

Fair Skin
Eyes of Beauty
Brows
KS Hairdo's

 If anyone is interested in using Jade to make a custom follower mod, I'm totally okay with that.
[quote]﻿[/quote]
[i][quote]"No more ugly presets" - Voldathyme[/quote][/i]
author: Voldathyme
